The paper focuses on e-commerce and customer satisfaction, which suggests a human-computer interaction (cs.HC) aspect. The proposed approach involves recommendation, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with organizing the configuration process, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and computer engineering (cs.CE). Finally, the paper proposes an interactive approach, which could fall under the category of social and information sciences (cs.SI).
